---
title: Mexican Crumbed Chicken Burger & Fries with Charred Corn Slaw & Mayonnaise
description: Have you been dreaming of a Mexican-flavoured crumbed chicken burger? Well how about that – so have we! And we promise you, it tastes even better in real life than we had imagined.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mexican-crumbed-chicken-burger-fries-9665dabf.jpg
